name: Spiral Eclipse
description: This composite image of the Lunar Eclipse of 27/07/18 was taken and processed by myself from Spain. Starting at top right and moving anti-clockwise, this shows the progression of the Lunar Eclipse at intervals from a bright full moon o the deep, dark, red of a total Lunar Eclipse. This piece would be an excellent choice for framing, digital or otherwise. Dimensions are 1103 x 991
